works.description:
From Easy Street to Modern Times, Charlie  
Chaplin has given us some of the funniest and most famous movies of all  
time. He is undoubtedly an icon of the silent film era. Here is a unique  
chance for his fans and car collectors to own a ride that once belonged to  
this Hollywood icon. Charlie Chaplin’s two-toned dual cowl long wheelbase  
1929 Pierce-Arrow has now appeared on eBay. By the 1920s, Chaplin was the  
most famous entertainer in the world, and his earnings were over $600,000 a  
year.
